  "description": "Sweet, sticky and inspired by the smoky flavours of the American South, this tasty pork dish has late summertime dining written all over it. You'll pan-fry (or barbecue!) pork loin steaks before coating them in a smoky homemade BBQ sauce. Served with paprika potatoes and a pickled salad. Smokin'!",
